boycott
üáµüá∏ Free Palestine.
My heart aches for the innocent lives lost, the children who will never grow up, the families torn apart, and the voices silenced. This is not just a political issue ‚Äî it is a human issue. No child should grow up under the sound of bombs. No mother should have to bury her baby. No people should be denied their right to live in peace, with dignity, and with justice.
We will not be silent. We will not turn away. We will continue to speak, to post, to pray, to boycott, and to educate ‚Äî because their lives matter. Because freedom is a right, not a privilege.
From the river to the sea, Palestine will be free.
